						<summary>

						<p>Stone in <hi rend="italic">basaru-kaṭṭa.</hi></p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1483, Durmati, Āshāḍha śu. 11</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1561 A.D., June 23, Monday.</hi></p>						

						<p>Damaged. Seems to record a gift of land to an Ārādhya (Brāhmaṇa) by Kōnēṭrājayyadēvamahārāja, son of Peṅnamarāja.</p>						

